        <p>All Leeds postcodes — Headingley, Roundhay, Horsforth, Chapel Allerton, Morley, Pudsey — plus Bradford, Wakefield, Huddersfield, Harrogate, and York. 1.9 million people across the West Yorkshire metro area. Full list on our <a href="/areas/">areas page</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How do I get started?</h3>
        <p><a href="/free-seo-audit-leeds/">Request a proposal</a>. We analyse your site, benchmark competitors, and deliver a prioritised action plan within 5 working days. No commitment required. <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> to begin.</p>
